{{Occupational hazards}}

'''控制等級'''（{{lang|en|Hierarchy of control}}），又名'''危害控制層級'''或'''安全控制措施順序'''等，是一套工業中用以減少或完全移除{{tsl|en|hazard (risk)|危害}}的系統<ref name="ohs handbook">{{cite web|url=http://ohshandbook.com.au/2012/01/20/how-the-hierarchy-of-control-can-help-you-fulfil-your-health-and-safety-duties/|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130114235809/http://ohshandbook.com.au/2012/01/20/how-the-hierarchy-of-control-can-help-you-fulfil-your-health-and-safety-duties/|url-status=dead|archive-date=2013-01-14|title=How the hierarchy of control can help you fulfil your health and safety duties|date=2012-01-20|publisher=Occupational Health & Safety Handbook|accessdate=2012-04-11}}</ref><ref name="safework south australia">{{cite web|url=http://www.safework.sa.gov.au/contentPages/EducationAndTraining/TrainingKits/WHSTrainingResourceKit/whsKit/top3_7.htm |title=Hierarchy of control diagram |website=Safework SA |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327051012/http://www.safework.sa.gov.au/contentPages/EducationAndTraining/TrainingKits/WHSTrainingResourceKit/whsKit/top3_7.htm |archive-date=2014-03-27 |url-status=dead |accessdate=2012-04-11 }}</ref>。此系統獲廣泛承認並用於各類安全管理組織。控制等級一般以倒置三角形表示，最上方者的效益最佳<ref name="saunions">{{cite web|url=http://www.saunions.org.au/ohs/hierachy_of_controls.htm|title=Hierarchy of Controls|last=|first=|date=|website=SA Unions|publisher=|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050623055058/http://www.saunions.org.au/ohs/hierachy_of_controls.htm|archive-date=2005-06-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>。一般而言，安全管理系統中會先作風險評估，再利用控制等級嘗試消除危害<ref name="worksafe victoria">{{cite web|url=http://www.worksafe.vic.gov.au/forms-and-publications/forms-and-publications/hazard-identification,-risk-assessment-and-risk-control-in-the-workplace |title=Hazard identification, risk assessment & risk control in the workplace |website=WorkSafe Victoria |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023101547/http://www.worksafe.vic.gov.au/forms-and-publications/forms-and-publications/hazard-identification%2C-risk-assessment-and-risk-control-in-the-workplace |archive-date=2013-10-23 |url-status=dead |accessdate=2012-04-11 }}</ref>。

控制等級將危害控制分類，按其效益較高者優先則可排列為：
* [[危害消除|危害消除]]
* {{tsl|en|Hazard substitution|危害替代}}
* {{tsl|en|Engineering controls|工程控制}}
* {{tsl|en|Administrative controls|行政控制}}
* [[個人防護裝備|個人防護裝備]]

== 控制等級的組成 ==
=== 危害消除 ===
{{Main article|危害消除}}
危害消除指將危害從系統及環境中完全移除，為最有效的安全控制措施<ref name="OHS answers" />。例如，將置於半空的物件改為地面，則可使員工高空工作的危害完全消除<ref name=NYCOSH />。

=== 危害替代 ===
{{Main article|危害替代}}
[[Image:DDTDichlordiphényltrichloréthane7.JPG|thumb]]，可以其他殺蟲劑取代]]

危害替代是第二有效的安全控制措施。其將現有會做成危害的物品或工序替換成不會做成危害或較少危害的物品或工序，例如以[[二氧化鈦|二氧化鈦]]取代{{tsl|en|lead paint|含鉛油漆}}。替代時應注意及考慮替代品會否帶來{{tsl|en|unintended consequences|意外後果}}<ref name="OHS answers" />。

=== 工程控制 ===
{{Main article|工程控制}}
工程控制不會減少現有危害，而是將危害與人隔離<ref name="NYCOSH">{{cite web|url=http://nycosh.org/index.php?page=Hierarchy-of-Hazard-Controls |title=Hierarchy of Hazard Controls |website=New York Committee for Occupational Safety & Health |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305133129/http://nycosh.org/index.php?page=Hierarchy-of-Hazard-Controls |archive-date=2012-03-05 |accessdate=2012-04-11 }}</ref>。例如工業用工具會設置護欄防止其運作時與人接觸，又或者高空工作時須設置工作平台防止人員墮下<ref name="OHS answers" />。此類措施一般較為昂貴，但長遠可降低成本<ref name="cdc">{{cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/engcontrols/|title=Engineering Controls|last=|first=|date=|website=U.S. National Institute for Occupational Safety and Health|publisher=|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318002244/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/engcontrols/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 行政控制 ===
[[File:2006-08-15_-_Road_Trip_-_Day_23_-_United_States_-_California_-_Monterey_-_Sign_-_Danger_Nature_-_17-_4889456702.jpg|警告牌指示切勿攀岩或下水，但無法避免其他人不小心忽略甚至特意違反]]
{{Main article|行政控制}}
行政控制改變人的工作模式，簡單例子為改變工作步驟、工作人員的訓練、規則與政策、警告標示等<ref name=NYCOSH />。行政控制不能消除危害，只可減少人員暴露於風險中的機會，而另一方面工作人員與其他人士亦可無意忽略甚至有意違反行政控制措施，使其變得無效，故其危害控制效益較低<ref name="OHS answers" />。

=== 個人防護裝備 ===
{{main|個人防護裝備}}
個人防護裝備（Personal protective equipment，常簡稱為PPE）包含工作服、[[口罩|口罩]]、[[安全帽|安全帽]]、{{tsl|en|high-visibility clothing|反光衣}}、{{tsl|en|Steel-toe boot|安全鞋}}等，為最低效益的安全控制措施，因這些裝備很有可能遭損毀或老化而變得無效，個人防護裝備亦未能為無關者提供保護<ref name="OHS answers">{{cite web|url=http://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/hsprograms/hazard_control.html|title=Hazard Control|last=|first=|date=2006-04-20|website=Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety|publisher=|accessdate=2012-04-11|archive-date=2020-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125214725/https://www.ccohs.ca/oshanswers/hsprograms/hazard_control.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。某些個人防護裝備亦會增加工作者的生理負擔，故亦需要額外訓練或檢查。

== 设计保障安全 ==
[[设计保障安全|设计保障安全]]為於設計階段已盡量減少危害的概念，而控制等級為其重要一環。设计保障安全着重於控制等級最高的部分，即危害消除與替代<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/hierarchy/default.html|title=CDC - Hierarchy of Controls - NIOSH Workplace Safety and Health Topic|website=www.cdc.gov|language=en-us|access-date=2017-08-07|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318024737/https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/topics/hierarchy/default.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

